    "causal_summary": "The `@spec-kit/mcp-server` build runs `prebuild` → `clean` → `rmSync('dist', {recursive,force})`, deleting the **live** `dist/` before `tsc --build` repopulates it over several seconds. Any running daemon that lazy-imports a module during that window hits `MODULE_NOT_FOUND` and crashes (RC-4 in packet 030). The wipe also deletes `dist/tsconfig.tsbuildinfo`, forcing a full (slow) recompile every time instead of an incremental one.",
